    "created_at": "2017-06-12T22:09:25Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-06-12T22:09:25Z",
    "body": "🇨🇳 🇹🇼 🇧🇷 🇪🇸 🇰🇷 🇯🇵 🇷🇺 🇫🇷 🇹🇭 🇳🇱 🇹🇷 🇮🇩 🇺🇦 🇨🇿 🇮🇹\r\n\r\nWe are moving forward with [Crowdin](https://crowdin.com/project/electron), a third-party translation service that facilitates crowdsource translations. It's pretty nifty.\r\n\r\nAnyone is welcome to join in the translation effort. For more details and info on how to help out, see this [electron/electron-i18n](https://github.com/electron/electron-i18n) repo.\r\n\r\nAs for the `docs-translations` directory: Even though it is incomplete and perpetually out of date, it is definitely still useful. I think we should leave that directory intact until we have a more complete alternative."
